== Overview ==
Purchase From [[Accolades Exchange]] In [[Talsian Warfront]].

== Where to Acquire ==
The Obliterator superweapon can be bought from the accolade exchanger in the Talsian Warfront, or found after defeating Annihilators in Sulphur (with squad [[Battle Merit|BM]] of 20m+).<ref>need to verify</ref> It can also be found in vaults in [[Praetorian Outpost|Praetorian Outposts]] in the [[South East Quadrant]] of [[Gamma]].
